<table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4"><tr bgcolor="#000000"><td><font color="#FFFFFF"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial" size="6">Friend of Wellisks</font></td></tr></table><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Author</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">cfbnv</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Description</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">An Orothe control deck that uses the somewhat neglected Orlon to remove, resuse, and just stomp the opponent into the ground.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Cards</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Magi:<br>
<!--626-->Voda<br>
(Starting: <!--459-->Submerge, <!--621-->Reef Hyren, <!--431-->C<!--344-->Oral Hyren)<br>
<br>
<!--449-->Orlon<br>
(Starting: <!--429-->Abaquist, <!--441-->Sea Barl, <!--459-->Submerge)<br>
<br>
<!--625-->Quilla<br>
(Starting: Usually <!--769-->Barqua&#39;s Bubble and <!--627-->Hubdra&#39;s Cube)<br>
<br>
Creatures(21):<br>
<!--763-->Deep <!--443-->Wellisk - 3<br>
<!--762-->Deep Barl - 3<br>
<!--443-->Wellisk - 3<br>
<!--441-->Sea Barl - 3<br>
<!--433-->Deep Hyren - 1<br>
<!--621-->Reef Hyren - 3<br>
